{
    "chapterId": "Act01_Chapter01_Trial",
    "lines": [
        {
            "id": "line_1",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "首先还原一下案发情况",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_2",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "死者囚犯C，被发现于早上6：50死于牢房中，死因为结果为死于心脏麻痹",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_3",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "clue_cause_of_death",
                "C的死因",
                "死因为心脏麻痹，但身上没有外伤，只有手和脸部混有不明纤维。",
                ""
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_4",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "验尸结果显示，C未遭受任何物理伤害，只有手和脸部混有不明纤维，尸体成一种奇怪的姿势死去",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长2",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_5",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "clue_death_posture",
                "C的死亡姿势",
                "尸体呈现一种奇怪的姿势，似乎在暗示什么。",
                ""
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_6",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "C囚有长期吸毒史，为了缓解戒断反应，每晚熄灯前都要注射药物",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长2",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_7",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "clue_medical_history",
                "C的病史与治疗",
                "C有长期吸毒史，每晚需要注射药物缓解戒断反应。",
                ""
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_8",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "（死因是心脏麻痹还有长期吸毒史吗......）",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_9",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "要我说答案已经很明显了把，嗑药把自己嗑死了呗",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_10",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "那死者的姿态该怎么解释？",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_11",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "问老子干嘛？我随口说说而已",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_12",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "（这样不行，得有一个讨论点）",
            "portrait": "Player/主角2",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_13",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": " 大家昨晚门禁前都在干什么？",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_14",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "昨晚我喝醉了记得不是很清楚...回房间的那会儿倒是撞见过C",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_15",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddEvidence",
            "parameters": [
                "clue_witness_a",
                "关于A看见的”C“",
                "A囚声称昨晚喝醉回房间时撞见过C。",
                ""
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_16",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "我就一直在看书",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_17",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "确保门禁前没有囚犯在外面，我就回了办公室。没有看过C",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_18",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "ShowChoice",
            "parameters": [
                "我昨天...来过这里但不记得干了什么|line_19",
                "（说谎）我昨晚回房间后一直待在房间里没见过C|line_24"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_19",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "我昨天...来过这里但不记得干了什么",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_20",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "哈？开什么玩笑！你就是凶手吧",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_21",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "我佩服你的勇气 我不得不怀疑你的动机",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_22",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "......",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_23",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["D", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_23_jump",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["trial_end"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_24",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "（说谎）我昨晚回房间后一直待在房间里没见过C",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_25",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "看来我们当中有人在说谎",
            "portrait": "Warden/审判动作",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_26",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "ShowChoice",
            "parameters": [
                "A|branch_a_start",
                "B|branch_b_start",
                "典狱长|branch_w_start"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_a_start",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "你在隐瞒什么，A？",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_27",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "哈！！？？",
            "portrait": "A/老囚2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_28",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "你回牢房那会儿C按道理正在注射药物怎么可能被你撞见？",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_29",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "这...该死！见鬼难道",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_30",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "呵呵，无稽之谈",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_31",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["A", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_32_jump_a",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["trial_end"]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_b_start",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "很明显B，你才是最可疑的那个",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_33",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "很遗憾，你的结论漏洞百出我想也没必要聊下去了",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_34",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "（啧，冷静下来不要急躁！）",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_35",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["D", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_36_jump_b",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["trial_end"]
        },
        {
            "id": "branch_w_start",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "典狱长，有一点你明显说得不对吧",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_37",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "D",
            "text": "通过锁上的痕迹就能知道，“那个”家伙可没乖乖呆在牢里，你的话语经不起推敲",
            "portrait": "Player/主角1",
            "position": "left"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_38",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "...你说的没错，但这是因为伪人很有可能改变身体形状逃了出去",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长2",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_39",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "B",
            "text": "可你却对这种可能不闻不问",
            "portrait": "B/盗窃犯2",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_40",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "A",
            "text": "你这家伙是同伙把？",
            "portrait": "A/老囚1",
            "position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_41",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "AddSuspicion",
            "parameters": ["典狱长", "25"]
        },
        {
            "id": "line_42_jump_w",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "Jump",
            "parameters": ["trial_end"]
        },
        {
            "id": "trial_end",
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": "典狱长",
            "text": "记录完成，下一轮。",
            "portrait": "Warden/典狱长1",
            "position": "center"
        },
        {
            "id": "line_44",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "LoadScene"
        }
    ]
}